1
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:19,680
Help! Someone save me!

2
00:00:19,680 --> 00:00:20,640
That's my voice.

3
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:23,480
Wenxin. What happened?

4
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:25,440
Who on earth wants to kill me?

5
00:00:26,680 --> 00:00:27,480
Chen Jian.

6
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:30,140
Strawberry Meowmeow.

7
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:31,890
Mother-in-law.

8
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:34,120
Have you heard the old saying,

9
00:00:34,120 --> 00:00:36,680
"don't back a dog into a corner

10
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:38,160
or it'll bite you"?

11
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:40,040
I need to end this quickly.

12
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,200
Feeling any better, Mom?

13
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:13,130
Much better than the last few days.

14
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:15,160
Where? Does it hurt here?

15
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:15,920
Yes.

16
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,810
Why are you back so late?

17
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:25,060
Where were you last night?

18
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,840
Mom is talking to you. Didn't you hear her?

19
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:32,440
I heard her. I just didn't want to answer.

20
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,580
What kind of attitude is that?

21
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:40,600
My son married you.

22
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,360
That really is a misfortune for this family.

23
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,759
Then let's get a divorce.

24
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,200
What did you say?

25
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,800
Your son is having an affair.

26
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,620
You didn't know that, did you?

27
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,479
What affair?

28
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,320
Don't talk nonsense.

29
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,240
It's fine.

30
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,410
You can confirm it with your son later.

31
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,200
Of course,

32
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:03,370
I also have the relevant evidence and materials.

33
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,660
It's too explicit,

34
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,650
so I won't show it to you.

35
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:09,090
Men have social engagements outside.

36
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,639
They are busy running around.

37
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:12,680
Your son is also about to go bankrupt.

38
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,880
You didn't know that either, did you?

39
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:16,600
What bankruptcy?

40
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,880
Don't talk nonsense.

41
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,480
Of course you don't know.

42
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:24,720
The company has been poorly managed for a long time,

43
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,380
and owes people a lot of money.

44
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,600
To pay off this debt,

45
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,160
your son has

46
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,760
tried every means possible.

47
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:42,160
Well, that's business.

48
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,770
There are losses and gains.

49
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,840
Let me tell you,

50
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,840
you can't divorce my son

51
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,920
just because he's broke.

52
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,780
You're not getting off that easy.

53
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:55,160
You were the one who brought up divorce.

54
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,079
Haven't you always wanted to be

55
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,280
the mistress of this house?

56
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,240
You said

57
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:02,210
there can only be one master of this house.

58
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,680
So from now on,

59
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,680
you are the master of this house.

60
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,520
Mrs. Chen.

61
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,600
By the way,

62
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,920
there's something I need to remind you of.

63
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:17,600
When I married your son,

64
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,440
he had nothing.

65
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,800
He was able to start the company

66
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,300
only because I helped him.

67
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,680
Honey.

68
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,890
Let me explain. I was wrong.

69
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,240
Don't talk to me.

70
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,920
You make me sick.

71
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,000
Sign the divorce papers.

72
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,760
This house is my pre-marital property.

73
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:46,840
I've contacted an agent to sell it.

74
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,920
Move out in three days, or else,

75
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,600
I'll call the police.

76
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,800
Jianjian.

77
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,320
Is she telling the truth?

78
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,760
Jianjian, don't be scared.

79
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,050
No matter what happens,

80
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,660
Mom is here for you.

81
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,860
He conspired with Strawberry Meow Meow to kill you.

82
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,159
Do you regret saving him?

83
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,120
I don't regret it.

84
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:11,880
Don't worry.

85
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,570
There's no one else.

86
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,400
Sit down.

87
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,360
What would you like to drink?

88
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:26,360
Don't worry, I won't live stream this time.

89
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,320
Speak.

90
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,490
Why did you call me here?

91
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,360
That look on your face...

92
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,400
makes it look like I'm the mistress.

93
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,520
I haven't been in contact with your husband.

94
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:45,580
It doesn't matter.

95
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,159
I've already filed for divorce.

96
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,920
If you like him,

97
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,080
you two can continue.

98
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,080
Did he agree?

99
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,240
When he cheated,

100
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:57,240
he didn't ask for my opinion either.

101
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:02,600
I don't have the time to listen to your business.

102
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:04,960
Really?

103
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,600
I thought regarding our affairs,

104
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,860
you'd want to be involved in everything.

105
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,720
I came to see you about something important.

106
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,760
Spit it out.

107
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,810
I don't have time for your chatter.

108
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,610
That shouldn't be the case.

109
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:21,020
You don't have a job right now.

110
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:23,180
You must have plenty of free time.

111
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,480
The huge insurance policy I bought before,

112
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,940
I've already canceled it.

113
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,640
You...

114
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,170
Why are you telling me this?

115
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,280
Still not answering.

116
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,040
She just won't pick up.

117
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,280
It's fine.

118
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,420
We still have her child, don't we?

119
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,560
I just feel

120
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,040
something is wrong.

121
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,400
Ever since that night...

122
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,000
You didn't take the revolving lantern, did you?

123
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,840
You go up first.

124
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:50,280
In case the driver can't reach you.

125
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,080
I'll go get it.

126
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:58,040
Wen Xin pushed the revolving lantern into the water herself.

127
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,370
There must be a problem.

128
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:00,760
It's fine.

129
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:03,160
We have so many revolving lanterns. Or,

130
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,900
we can ask the Wen Xin from twelve days later.

131
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,210
I tried them all yesterday.

132
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,160
But she just won't answer the phone.

133
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,520
Did she really tell you that?

134
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,720
Yes.

135
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:35,380
The accident insurance beneficiary has been changed.

136
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,600
I had a nightmare.

137
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,900
Don't take it to heart.

138
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:40,980
Everyone has nightmares.

139
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:43,140
Let's get a divorce, then.

140
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,520
Your son cheated.

141
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,000
This house is my pre-marital property.

142
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,960
I've contacted an agent to sell it.

143
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:51,240
What should we do now?

144
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,520
Quiet.

145
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,200
I keep feeling

146
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:59,720
like Wenxin knows everything.

147
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,840
You are Chen Jian.

148
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,320
Who?

149
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,320
Who is speaking?

150
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,320
I am you,

151
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,240
Chen Jian,

152
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:10,320
the you from 12 days later.
